374
00:40:40.494 --> 00:40:41.985
Quel mois sommes-nous ?

375
00:40:42.455 --> 00:40:44.572
Je suis Samantha Gaynor.

376
00:40:45.624 --> 00:40:47.365
Carol Akers.

377
00:40:47.710 --> 00:40:50.248
